天文学家可以通过星迹来判断望远镜天文台选址的质量。[[北极星|北极星]]的星迹观测可以用于检测大气[[视宁度|视宁度]]及望远镜支架系统的振动。<ref name='harlan_site_testing'> {{cite journal | title = A Star-Trail Telescope for Astronomical Site-Testing | journal = Publications of the Astronomical Society of the Pacific | date = 1965-08 | first = E.A. | last = Harlan | coauthors = Merle F. Walker | volume = 77 | issue = 457 | pages = 246–252| doi = 10.1086/128210 | url = http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/1965PASP...77..246H}}</ref>该方法由E.S. Skinner在1931年所著的''天空摄影手册''（''A Manual of Celestial Photography''）一书中首次提出。<ref>{{cite book | last1 = King | first1 = Edward Skinner | title = A Manual of Celestial Photography | publisher = Eastern Science Supply Co | year = 1931 | location = Boston, Massachusetts | page = 37 | url = http://books.google.com/books?id=JT-xAAAAIAAJ&dq=editions:coHm8MaIiNwC | access-date = 2013-04-04 | archive-date = 2014-01-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140105063302/http://books.google.com/books?id=JT-xAAAAIAAJ&dq=editions:coHm8MaIiNwC | dead-url = no }}</ref>

